{"tid":2208804,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國紐約州發生槍擊案至少13人中槍，其中2人死亡","createTime":"2020-09-19T07:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T08:08:05.000Z","uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d99174aeb5549fc90262fdc1c41871891f50033","tid":2208804,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"2020-09-19 15:47<br />\n當地時間19日凌晨，美國紐約州羅切斯特市（Rochester）發生大規模槍擊案，至少13人中槍，其中2人在現場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約郵報》報道，槍擊案發生在凌晨0點30分。警員接報后來到古德曼街（Goodman Street）及賓夕法尼亞大道（Pennsylvania Avenue）交界處。現場目擊者稱&ldquo;槍聲非常密集&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n目前關於該事件的細節認不清楚，當地警方預計將在19日上午召開新聞發布會公布更多內容。"},{"pid":"2122752c8538f0427c2b67132c71018b69de6116","tid":2208804,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:54:46.000Z","msg":"又係democrat"},{"pid":"fb9da7d3f084f481a099a8289b554b72f1870001","tid":2208804,"uid":127575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2122752c8538f0427c2b67132c71018b69de6116","tid":2208804,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:54:46.000Z","msg":"又係democrat"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:01:21.000Z","msg":"點解永遠都係民主黨出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜又係你呀民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明顯睇得出有咩黨管治就會有咩結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c298f3e9c51957c26c1e35d382274a8bac8246","tid":2208804,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb9da7d3f084f481a099a8289b554b72f1870001","tid":2208804,"uid":127575,